```plantuml
@startuml jinnerbichler_flash-home

actor User
participant "Home Assistant" as HA
participant "Coffee Client" as CC
participant "Flash Server (Coffee Machine)" as FSCM
participant "Flash Server (Provider)" as FSP
participant "IOTA Tangle" as Tangle

User -> HA: Triggers "Make Coffee"
HA -> CC: MQTT Publish (make_coffee)
CC -> FSCM: HTTP Request (create payment)
FSCM -> FSP: HTTP Request (initiate channel)
FSP -> FSCM: HTTP Response (channel details)
FSCM -> CC: HTTP Response (payment request)
CC -> FSCM: HTTP Request (signed payment)
FSCM -> FSP: HTTP Request (verify payment)
FSP -> Tangle: Submit transaction
Tangle -> FSP: Transaction confirmed
FSP -> FSCM: HTTP Response (payment confirmed)
FSCM -> CC: HTTP Response (confirmation)
CC -> HA: MQTT Publish (status update)
HA -> User: UI Update (coffee ready)

@enduml
```